data.description: Tired of the Boring and Basic?  Look no more!  This 3 bed, 3 Full bath home has more style and flare than anything else for sale! Click thru the pictures to see your new covered back deck or in your HOT TUB overlooking the woods, a fenced yard with a shed, and the most amazing finished LL with entertaining space in the neighborhood!  Think Marilyn Monroe meets Al Capone in the media/bar/game/bourbon room. Numerous updates in this one owner Ranch, even the garage has an epoxy floor and the trash cans have their own special storage.  Truly a must see!
